DESCRIPTIONS:
This is a fist sized aquamarine, priced indeed for its colour intensity.
LORE:
Oceanic energy is belived to be contained within these stones and its said to bring sailors unmatched bravery and the power to overcome the worse of storms.
Some also say it banish fear, calms nerves and impart strength and control to the wearer.
A common saying is that a particular shiprunner on the pirats island owns a gem the size of a human head and all who seek it will end up dead, such is the magic of the gem
